    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>In archaeology, the reordering of available remains digitally to virtually reassemble something that existed in the past.This process makes a 3D model assembling surveyed fragments, present in the excavation site, with elements philologically reconstructed on the basis of historical knowledge and documentation.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
